'''2010年斯里兰卡总统选举'''是历史上第六次[[斯里兰卡总统|斯里兰卡总统]]选举，由[[马欣达·拉贾帕克萨|马欣达·拉贾帕克萨]]胜出。<ref name='news.lk-election'>{{cite news | title=President decides to hold the Presidential Election | date=2009-11-23 | url=http://news.lk/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=12489&Itemid=44 | work=Government Information Department | accessdate=2009-11-23 | archive-date=2017-11-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171116082920/https://news.lk/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=12489&Itemid=44 | dead-url=no }}</ref>2009年12月17日截止接受提名，选举于2010年1月26日举行。<ref name='st-5candidates'>{{cite news | title=5 candidates in the fray | date=2009-11-29 | url=http://www.sundaytimes.lk/091129/News/nws_04.html | work=The Sunday Times | accessdate=2009-11-26 | archive-date=2018-03-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180327212359/http://www.sundaytimes.lk/091129/News/nws_04.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>
